      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend the Controlled Substances Act to require dispensers of certain opioids and opiates to affix on the container or package thereof a clear, concise warning that the opioid or opiate can cause dependence, addiction, and overdose, and for other purposes.</title>
